[Reuters update of 18 Jul 2002 says: "The number of German farms banned
from selling their meat and milk, after receiving animal feed tainted with
a banned hormone, has now risen to around 2100 from 300, German authorities
said on Thursday." It seems that this multi-routed food scare is gaining
pace, with a lot at stake. Again - food (water) for thought. - Mod.AS]
